with temp as (SELECT distinct sold_to_cust_num, f.sw_sbscrptn_id, line_of_bus_code, line_of_bus_code_dscr, sap_ctrct_num, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, mnged_entmt_prog FROM ENTL1.ENTMT_SUM_FACT f LEFT OUTER JOIN rshr2.sw_sbscrptn_id_part_num_xref x ON x.SW_SBSCRPTN_ID=f.SW_SBSCRPTN_ID where f.MOD_DATE > '#LAST_ESF_TS#' and f.MOD_DATE<= '#CUR_ESF_TS#' )
, temp2 as ( SELECT --sap_sales_org_code, sold_to_cust_num, sw_sbscrptn_id, line_of_bus_code, line_of_bus_code_dscr, sap_ctrct_num, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, CAST(sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'LIC' AND Curr_Period_Flag IN ('A', 'F') THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS lic_subscrptn_id_qty, CAST(sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'SNS' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'A' THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS actv_sns_sbscrptn_id_qty, CAST( sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'SNS' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'F' THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS future_sns_sbscrptn_id_qty, CAST(sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'FIXTERM' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'A' THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS fixterm_sbscrptn_id_qty, CAST(sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'MTHLYLIC' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'A' THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS mthly_lic_sbscrptn_id_qty, CAST(sum(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'SAAS' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'A' THEN COALESCE(NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY,0) ELSE 0 END) as DECIMAL(15,3)) AS saas_sbscrptn_id_qty, MAX(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'SNS' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'A' AND (COUNTOF-zero_qty_flag) > 0 THEN CASE WHEN (COUNTOF-zero_qty_flag) > 1 THEN 'Multiple' ELSE CHAR(end_date) END ELSE '' END) AS ACTV_SNS_END_DATE, MAX(CASE WHEN entmt_sys_revn_stream_cat_code = 'SNS' AND Curr_Period_Flag = 'F' AND (COUNTOF-zero_qty_flag) > 0 THEN CASE WHEN (COUNTOF-zero_qty_flag) > 1 THEN 'Multiple' ELSE CHAR(end_date) end ELSE '' END) AS future_sns_end_date, mnged_entmt_prog, current timestamp as ts FROM ( SELECT --Sap_Sales_Org_Code, f.Sold_To_Cust_Num, f.Sw_Sbscrptn_Id, f.line_of_bus_code, f.line_of_bus_code_dscr, f.Sap_Ctrct_Num, f.ENTMT_SYS_REVN_STREAM_CAT_CODE, CASE WHEN end_date < CURRENT DATE THEN 'P' WHEN start_date > CURRENT DATE THEN 'F' ELSE 'A' END Curr_Period_Flag, SUM (NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY) AS NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY, MAX (CASE WHEN NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY<>0 THEN end_date ELSE '1900-01-01 00:00:00.000000' END) AS end_date, COUNT (DISTINCT (CASE WHEN NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY<>0 THEN end_date ELSE '1900-01-01 00:00:00.000000' END)) AS countof, MAX (CASE WHEN NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY<>0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS zero_qty_flag, x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, f.mnged_entmt_prog FROM ENTL1.ENTMT_SUM_FACT f INNER JOIN temp t ON f.sold_to_cust_num=t.sold_to_cust_num and f.sw_sbscrptn_id=t.sw_sbscrptn_id and f.line_of_bus_code=t.line_of_bus_code and f.line_of_bus_code_dscr=t.line_of_bus_code_dscr and f.sap_ctrct_num=t.sap_ctrct_num and f.mnged_entmt_prog=t.mnged_entmt_prog LEFT OUTER JOIN rshr2.sw_sbscrptn_id_part_num_xref x ON f.SW_SBSCRPTN_ID=x.SW_SBSCRPTN_ID and COALESCE(x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE,'')=COALESCE(t.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE,'') and COALESCE(x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR,'')=COALESCE(t.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR,'') where f.INACT_FLAG=0 GROUP BY --Sap_Sales_Org_Code, f.Sold_To_Cust_Num, f.Sw_Sbscrptn_Id, f.line_of_bus_code, f.line_of_bus_code_dscr, f.Sap_Ctrct_Num, x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, x.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, f.ENTMT_SYS_REVN_STREAM_CAT_CODE, f.mnged_entmt_prog, CASE WHEN end_date < CURRENT DATE THEN 'P' WHEN start_date > CURRENT DATE THEN 'F' ELSE 'A' END )
group by --sap_sales_org_code, sold_to_cust_num, sw_sbscrptn_id, line_of_bus_code, line_of_bus_code_dscr, sap_ctrct_num, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, mnged_entmt_prog )
,temp3 as (select distinct Sold_To_Cust_Num,Sw_Sbscrptn_Id,Mnged_Entmt_Prog,Sap_Ctrct_Num, case when ENTMT_SYS_REVN_STREAM_CAT_CODE in ('LIC','SNS','FIXTERM','OTHER') then 1 when ENTMT_SYS_REVN_STREAM_CAT_CODE='MTHLYLIC' then 10 when ENTMT_SYS_REVN_STREAM_CAT_CODE='SAAS' then 100 end as RSC_CODE_NUM from ENTL1.ENTMT_SUM_FACT)
,temp4 as (select Sold_To_Cust_Num,Sw_Sbscrptn_Id,Mnged_Entmt_Prog,Sap_Ctrct_Num,sum(RSC_CODE_NUM) RSC_CODE_NUM_SUM from temp3 group by Sold_To_Cust_Num,Sw_Sbscrptn_Id,Mnged_Entmt_Prog,Sap_Ctrct_Num)
,temp5 as --added by susie on July 27 2016 ( select Sold_To_Cust_Num,Sw_Sbscrptn_Id,Mnged_Entmt_Prog,Sap_Ctrct_Num ,min(start_date) as MIN_SNS_Start_Date from ENTL1.ENTMT_SUM_FACT ESF where ESF.START_DATE <> '1900-01-01' AND ESF.NET_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY <> 0 group by Sold_To_Cust_Num,Sw_Sbscrptn_Id,Mnged_Entmt_Prog,Sap_Ctrct_Num )
SELECT temp2.Sold_To_Cust_Num, temp2.sw_sbscrptn_id, temp2.line_of_bus_code, temp2.line_of_bus_code_dscr, temp2.sap_ctrct_num, temp2.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, temp2.ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, temp2.lic_subscrptn_id_qty, temp2.actv_sns_sbscrptn_id_qty, temp2.future_sns_sbscrptn_id_qty, temp2.fixterm_sbscrptn_id_qty, temp2.mthly_lic_sbscrptn_id_qty, temp2.saas_sbscrptn_id_qty, temp2.ACTV_SNS_END_DATE, temp2.future_sns_end_date, temp2.mnged_entmt_prog, temp2.ts, CASE WHEN temp4.RSC_CODE_NUM_SUM=100 THEN 'SAAS' WHEN temp4.RSC_CODE_NUM_SUM=10 THEN 'MTHLYLIC' WHEN temp4.RSC_CODE_NUM_SUM=1 THEN 'PRPETUAL' WHEN temp4.RSC_CODE_NUM_SUM=11 THEN 'PRPETML' END AS Cust_Prod_Portfolio_Code, temp5.MIN_SNS_Start_Date
FROM temp2 LEFT OUTER JOIN temp4 ON (temp2.Sold_To_Cust_Num=temp4.Sold_To_Cust_Num AND temp2.sw_sbscrptn_id=temp4.sw_sbscrptn_id AND temp2.sap_ctrct_num=temp4.sap_ctrct_num AND temp2.mnged_entmt_prog=temp4.mnged_entmt_prog)
-- added by susie on July 27 2016
LEFT OUTER JOIN temp5 ON (temp2.Sold_To_Cust_Num=temp5.Sold_To_Cust_Num AND temp2.sw_sbscrptn_id=temp5.sw_sbscrptn_id AND temp2.sap_ctrct_num=temp5.sap_ctrct_num AND temp2.mnged_entmt_prog=temp5.mnged_entmt_prog)

CREATE TABLE ENTL1.Entmt_Sum_Fact_Flat ( SOLD_TO_CUST_NUM CHAR(10) NOT NULL, SW_SBSCRPTN_ID CHAR(12) NOT NULL, LINE_OF_BUS_CODE CHAR(2) NOT NULL, LINE_OF_BUS_CODE_DSCR CHAR(40) NOT NULL, SAP_CTRCT_NUM CHAR(10) NOT NULL, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE CHAR(8) NOT NULL, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, MNGED_ENTMT_PROG CHAR(5) NOT NULL, ADD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, ADD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL, MOD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, MOD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL, LIC_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, ACTV_SNS_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, FUTR_SNS_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, FIXTERM_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, MTHLY_LIC_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, SAAS_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3) NOT NULL, ACTV_SNS_END_DATE CHAR(10), FUTR_SNS_END_DATE CHAR(10), MAX_SNS_END_DATE DATE, MAX_SNS_SBSCRPTN_ID_QTY DECIMAL(15,3), CUST_PROD_PORTFOLIO_CODE CHAR(8), LES_ENTMT_STAT_CODE CHAR(8), Earliest_Start_Date DATE , PRIMARY KEY (SOLD_TO_CUST_NUM, SW_SBSCRPTN_ID, LINE_OF_BUS_CODE, LINE_OF_BUS_CODE_DSCR, SAP_CTRCT_NUM, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE, ALT_SW_PROD_BRAND_CODE_DSCR, MNGED_ENTMT_PROG) )
